channel.title: 718 - 24/7 - VPS - Eco - Nex - Custom
channel.description:
Hello there, My friend and I have been working very hard on an RSPS for our gaming community called ProjectFatality, we've released a Garry's Mod server which has been quite a success and we've chosen to expand. We are still working on this RSPS, however it has reached a point where a large majority of the bugs are fixed and we can now release to the public. We're waiting on a domain to register with our website and as I said, we're still working on the server. I admit that it is a Matrix source, however I promise to make it unique unlike many other RSPS's. PS: [size=6] We Need Staff [/size] If you'd like to download the client, here's a link: [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?22puwtkzg7ckhw1]http://www.mediafire.com/?22puwtkzg7ckhw1[/url] We also have a webclient however we're waiting for domain to register: [url=http://192.95.2.139/client.html]http://192.95.2.139/client.html[/url] And here's are forums for the time being: [url=http://www.projectfatality.enjin.com]http://www.projectfatality.enjin.com[/url] Screen Shots: [IMG]http://img62.imageshack.us/img62/6239/99340f2a40e640758be58d0.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/WVWWsQg.png[/img] [IMG]http://img7.imageshack.us/img7/5867/5bcd43771c8446aca1e02da.png[/img]
